# Add the details of each connected, active and disconnected clients to the server
* When a client connects to a port, request and log that to the server before let the client actually connect to it
* When a client disconnects from the server, log the active time and messages to the server
* THe server should capable of disconnecting any socket anytime it wants
* The server can also suspend its connection to a socket and resume it anytime it wants
* The server should give a client a MAX_TIME to reply before terminating the connection after giving the last reply